Patricia Carry Stewart, vice president of the Edna McConnell Clark Foundation, was elected a director of this retailer.
The board expands to 14 members.
Frederick A. Postelle was elected vice president of human resources, effective Jan. 1.
He will succeed Ira H. Peterman, who is retiring.
Mr. Postelle is currently senior vice president of human resources at the company's Marshalls division. 

